></span></span></span></span> )。</p><p> <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Pi_{n+1}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Π</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>资产<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\forall x, P(x)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∀</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>需要一个由发行人在每个时间点选择的计数器<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x\in\mathbb{N}"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∈</span></span> <span class="mjx-texatom MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">N</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，以及具有相同持有者和发行人的标的<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Sigma_n"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>资产<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P(x)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> （如果没有计数器）选择时，标的资产为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\top"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊤</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> )。</p><p>如果标的资产曾经被出售或赠送，则必须在下次更新之前重新购买。</p></blockquote><p>这种（任一）表述都存在几个明显的问题，实际上可以归结为两件事：</p><ul><li><i>建设成本——</i>你<i>想</i>赌一种获胜策略的存在，但你实际上赌的是你（或市场上的任何人）是否会找到一种获胜策略。特别是，这意味着“找到获胜策略的成本”听起来可能对资产的价格很重要，而且持有和发行资产的任务本身就是战略性的，因此设计一个基于库存的做市商（例如 LMSR）。</li><li><i>偿付能力/战略破产</i>——交易者不再承担有限责任，他们并不真正拥有他们声称拥有的现金（如果他们再次输掉比赛，他们可能必须随时偿还）。给定一个代理人，其资产的基础价值为 $1、$0、$1、$1、$0、$1...，您如何确定该资产的“真实”价值是多少？在市场中，真正执行假设激励（即代理人实际上关心金钱）的是<i>预算</i>机制，又名<i>资本主义</i><span class="footnote-reference" role="doc-noteref" id="fnrefvkihqojlvys"><sup><a href="#fnvkihqojlvys">[2]</a></sup></span> ，它让那些已经证明自己擅长利润最大化的代理人获得更大的影响力，如用一个叫做“财富”的变量来衡量。这种“资本主义”确实使我们能够将市场带到这样的环境：交易者不被认为是完美的利润最大化代理人，而只是一些程序。现在，当交易者像传统预测市场一样承担有限责任时（即他们实际上持有他们所拥有的资产，并且永远不会被要求归还），检查他们是否在预算之内很容易：只需检查他们当前现金的价值储备。此外，你仍然可以只关注利润最大化的代理人，并仍然研究有趣的事情：现在不再这样了，当没有办法定义代理人对特定价值序列的重视程度，而不求助于“资本主义是什么样的代理人”选择为？”。</li></ul><hr><h2><strong>建构主义</strong></h2><p>后一个问题可以暂时放在一边，通过让游戏一次性进行，即让智能体一次性选择他们的一组选择，而不是让他们无限期地添加它（显式构造<span class="footnote-reference" role="doc-noteref" id="fnrefpugs3qpv0an"><sup><a href="#fnpugs3qpv0an">[3]</a></sup></span> ）</p><p>我认为，第一个问题意味着对我们给出句子的概率进行某种彻底的重新思考。就像逻辑不确定性要求我们接受给予<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\pi_{10^{99}}=6"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base" style="margin-right: -0.003em;"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.003em;">π</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.445em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">10</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 83.3%; vertical-align: 0.443em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.06em;"><span class="mjx-texatom" style=""><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">99</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">6</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的不是 0 或 1 的概率一样——通过将知识与一类程序相对化——<i>建构主义</i>要求我们接受非 VF 句子被解读为的概率:</p><blockquote><p><i>我们将构造</i>一个<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x 的</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>概率，使得对于所有<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="y"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><i>我们将构造</i><span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P(x,y)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p></blockquote><p>正如我所说，<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Constructivism_(philosophy_of_mathematics)"><i>建构主义的</i></a>立场是，对非 VF 句子有效的唯一信息是帮助你赢得 VF 游戏的信息。如果你很难构造一个<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>来玩，那么这应该计入句子的概率。不过，这并不像人们想象的那么可怕，因为你确实拥有整个市场的能力。</p><p>我现在将提供一些结果来说服您这种方法是好的。为此目的，关注统计而不是算法的不确定性可能更容易。具体来说，我所说的是一些索引为<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P(x,y)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的随机变量序列；则<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bigcup_x P(x, 5)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-munderover"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">⋃</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.438em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">5</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>是一个<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Sigma_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>句子； <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bigcup_x \bigcap_y P(x,y)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-munderover"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">⋃</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.438em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-munderover MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size1-R" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">⋂</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.438em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>是<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Sigma_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>等。请注意，如果<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P(x,y)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>是独立的，则任何<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Sigma_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Σ</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>或<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Pi_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Π</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>或更高句子的概率必须为 0 或 1根据<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kolmogorov%27s_zero%E2%80%93one_law">柯尔莫哥洛夫 0-1 定律</a>；所以你必须引入它们之间的依赖关系。例如</p><blockquote><p>生成每个<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P(x, 0)\sim \operatorname{Bernoulli}\left(\frac1{(x+1)^2}\right)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">0</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">∼</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">Bernoulli</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char"></span></span> <span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-size3-R" style="padding-top: 1.256em; padding-bottom: 1.256em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mfrac"><span class="mjx-box MJXc-stacked" style="width: 2.324em; padding: 0px 0.12em;"><span class="mjx-numerator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 3.286em; top: -1.372em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-denominator" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 3.286em; bottom: -1.089em;"><span class="mjx-mrow" style=""><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">+</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mo"><span c